1
00:00:15,715 --> 00:00:19,742
Celebrating 60 Years of the Kadokawa Group

2
00:00:29,529 --> 00:00:32,726
Is anyone here?

3
00:00:39,973 --> 00:00:40,905
Dad...

4
00:00:43,510 --> 00:00:44,636
Sis...

5
00:00:51,818 --> 00:00:53,080
...don't go.

6
00:01:15,108 --> 00:01:16,598
I had a nightmare.

7
00:01:17,644 --> 00:01:21,546
Tokyo, where I was born, was in ruins.

8
00:01:23,516 --> 00:01:27,646
Are you going to sleep all day?
You'll be late for school!

9
00:01:32,425 --> 00:01:35,519
Tadashi, get up!

10
00:01:43,403 --> 00:01:46,702
It had been six months since the divorce.

11
00:01:49,209 --> 00:01:54,613
From the window of the room Grandpa built for me...

12
00:01:54,681 --> 00:01:56,546
...the sea was calm.

13
00:02:05,725 --> 00:02:10,287
That summer, I fell in love for the first time.

14
00:02:11,698 --> 00:02:12,790
And...

15
00:02:15,034 --> 00:02:16,934
...I told a little white lie.

16
00:02:40,109 --> 00:02:41,269
What's that?!

17
00:03:01,297 --> 00:03:06,496
Horror... horror...

18
00:03:07,303 --> 00:03:13,037
There's a horrible war...

19
00:03:15,078 --> 00:03:16,545
...coming!

20
00:03:29,125 --> 00:03:33,255
The time has come... now is the time of revenge.

21
00:03:34,631 --> 00:03:36,895
O ye things humanity has used and discarded...

22
00:03:36,966 --> 00:03:39,434
O spirits persecuted...

23
00:03:41,170 --> 00:03:44,071
O rage shut away...

24
00:03:44,641 --> 00:03:47,075
...arise.

25
00:03:49,646 --> 00:03:52,809
It's time to arise!

26
00:04:01,157 --> 00:04:02,249
Arise.

27
00:04:11,734 --> 00:04:13,497
Join with us.

28
00:04:45,168 --> 00:04:48,296
Arise, O vengeful wraith...

29
00:04:49,973 --> 00:04:51,201
...Yomotsumono!

30
